data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom 2 bath POOL home located on over a quarter acre lot in south Lakeland.  Not only are you in a neighborhood that has NO HOA fees but you will also live on a road with a cul del sac on one side, so NO THRU TRAFFIC!  When you walk in to the home you will be greeted by the first of TWO family rooms.  In the kitchen you will have plenty of counter space for cooking and room for a table to eat at.  Right off the kitchen you will find the second family room that offers a beautiful wood burning fireplace to cozy up next to on those cold nights or mornings.  As you look throughout the home you will find 3 bedrooms as well as two bathrooms.  In one bathroom you will see that it offers a tub for soaking and the other offers the convenience of a walk in shower.  As you make your way outside you will pleased to see that not only do you have a screened in porch to enjoy the outdoors without the bugs, but a fully screened inground pool to take a dip on those hot summer days or nights.  Need a workspace?  This home not only offers a one car garage attached to the home but also a fully enclosed large workshop in the backyard.  The added bonuses don't stop there.  You will also find a fantastic oversize aluminum pole barn in the backyard to house all your toys.  All these great things this home offers AND you won't have to worry about replacing an AC unit and handler here in Florida because this one is LESS THAN A YEAR OLD!  Schedule your showing today and come see for yourself all this home has to offer.    No Assignable Contracts
